channel.title: Lil question... >.<
channel.description:
i make changes to my client.java file and save them, then run the compiler, but then no changes are made to my server :confused:
its doesnt say anything about any errors it just doesnt do anything
anybody know what im doin wrong?

item.title: Lil question... >.<
item.dc:creator: @Drunk_On_Java Drunk On Java
item.description:
@Drunk_On_Java wrote:

Download jdk1.5.0_07. Then make a .bat file that says this: (to make a .bat files, open notepad and save as *.bat)

@ECHO OFF
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_07\bin\javac.exe" client.java

And then run it and it will compile.
